<h2 id=3D"SD:PaymentsLimitsChannels-ImpactedSystemSummary"><span>Impacted S=
ystem Summary</span></h2>
<p><br><br><strong>Impacted System Images</strong></p>
<p>=E2=AD=90 - Change&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp=
; =F0=9F=9F=A9 - New&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span c=
lass=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">=F0=9F=94=B5<span>&nbsp;</span></span>- Exi=
sting Implementation &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span>=
&nbsp;</span>:cross:<span>&nbsp;</span>- Decommission</p>
<p><br></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"wrapped confluenceTable">
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Cash Platform (<span class=3D"ui-provider gs b c d e f g h i j k l m n o=
 p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">A014A6</span>)</p></th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>=E2=AD=90</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><=
br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><strong>Payments MFE</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Generate a new unique <span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">Instruction=
 Trace Id for payments(only applicable for payments and <span class=3D"inli=
ne-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"e88b45d2-fdb0-40ee-ab69-07315d78538d">not fo=
r transfe</span>rs) and include this new Id in the payment request as part =
of POST /payments Exp API call on click of "Send for authorisation"</span><=
/li>
<li><span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">In the "Payment Details" page, di=
splay the Payment limits(checker cumulative limit &amp; Organisation Channe=
l cumulative limit) by consuming POST /retrievePaymentLimits Exp API Call</=
span></li>
<li>On the "Payment Details" page=20
<ul>
<li>Validate the following Payment <span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" da=
ta-ref=3D"1cb2ae60-22a0-40da-a4dc-a10358e4e893">Limits(by consuming validat=
e limit Exp</span> API route) on click of "Authorise" button=20
<ul>
<li>Individual Checker Transaction Limit</li>
<li>Individual Checker Cumulative Limit</li>
<li>Organisational Channels Cumulative Limit</li>
<li>NPP or DE Transaction Limit(based on scheme/payment method)</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Submit the payment request for Authorisation(on "Authorise" button clic=
k) only if none of the above payment limits are reached</li>
</ul></li>
</ul><p><strong>Payments Exp API</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Update POST /payments Exp API request to include new request attribute =
"i<span style=3D"color: rgb(23,43,77);">nstructionTraceId". This attributed=
 will be used &amp; validated when calling Payment Limits CAP API and also =
when the payment is being processed by the Payment Initiation CAP API.</spa=
n></li>
<li>Expose a new Exp API route to fetch the payment limits. This new route =
will consume the Payment Limit CAP API to fetch the payment limits from Lim=
its DB.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Expose a new Exp API route to validate the Payment Limits. This new rou=
te will consume the Payment Limit CAP API to carry out the required payment=
 limit validations.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</thead>
<colgroup class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
<col class=3D"">
</colgroup>
</table>
