<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
As part of MVP, should we display remaining Checker cumulative &amp; Organi=
sation Channel cumulative limit to Checker on the "Payment Details" page wh=
en approving the request??</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"5523a878-80cd-44c5-8433-0=
a4fce77dce1">Yes, displaying Cumulative limits on Payment Details page is i=
n scope for MVP</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span data-teams=3D"true"><span class=3D"fui-StyledText ___rj1mvc0 fyind=
8e f1k6fduh fdvs7vj fx5ovu0"><a class=3D"confluence-userlink user-mention" =
