-hasbody=3D"false" data-macro-name=3D"status">&nbsp;DONE</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Ability to display the remaining checker cumulative limit &amp; organisatio=
n channel cumulative limit to checkers when approving the workflow request.=
</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
:tick:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
When checker is approving a payment workflow request, display the remaining=
 checker cumulative limit &amp; organisation channel cumulative limit on "P=
ayment Details" page so that the checker can make an informed decision prio=
r to approving the respective payment workflow request.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Documentation:<span>&nbsp;</span>:tick:</p></td>
