<div class=3D"content-wrapper">
<p><span class=3D"status-macro aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-success conf-macro o=
utput-inline" style=3D"color: rgb(255,255,255);text-decoration: none;" data=
-hasbody=3D"false" data-macro-name=3D"status">DONE</span></p>
</div></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Ability to validate the payment limits when checker is approving the paymen=
t request from Payment details page</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
:tick:</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ul>
<li>When the checker is approving the payment request, validate the followi=
ng payment limits against the Payment Limit CAP API even before submitting =
the payment request for approval,=20
<ul>
<li>Individual Checker Transaction Limit</li>
<li>NPP or DE Transaction Limit(based on scheme/payment method)</li>
<li>Individual Checker Cumulative Limit</li>
<li>Organisational Channels Cumulative Limit</li>
</ul></li>
<li>Payment request will only be submitted for approval if none of the abov=
e payment limits are reached/breached</li>
</ul></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>Documentation:<span>&nbsp;</span>:tick:</p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><br></p></td>
